title: ROBOCOP - LAST STAND 02 (of 08) (2013) (Boom) (Digital) (JK-Empi
description:
Robocop Last Stand #2 (of 8)
	
By: Frank Miller, Steven Grant, Korkut Oztekin	
Genre: Science-Fiction
Publisher: Boom! Studios	
Pub. Date: September 11, 2013
For ages: 16+

ROBOCOP'S LAST STAND, AS FRANK MILLER INTENDED. Robocop must defend the people of Detroit as a fighter for justice and a symbol for resistance.

But will that be enough to prevent its hostile takeover and destruction? With the help of his newfound, beautiful and mysterious ally, Marie, he may have a chance.
